        "content": "<p><strong>dhil</strong> requested <a href=\"https://github.com/alexcrichton\">alexcrichton</a> for a review on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/11717\">PR #11717</a>.</p>",
